<h1><span id="Halloween_Gambit">Halloween Gambit</span></h1>
<p>The Halloween or Müller-Schulze Gambit is an aggressive and complex gambit. White sacrifices a piece with the idea of central pawn storm, with the possibility of gaining time by driving back the black knights.
</p>
<p><br><b>1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Nxe5</b>
</p>
